(30, 'Công Ty TNHH Asiasoft', '', '', NULL, ' Asiasoft Company Limited was founded in Vietnam in 2004 with the primary objective of providing service, support and as well as promoting online contents in...Chi tiết\r\n						Asiasoft Company Limited was founded in Vietnam in 2004 with the primary objective of providing service, support and as well as promoting online contents in Vietnam. Asiasoft’s core business covers the publishing of Online Massive Multiplayer Games, Multiplayer Online Games, Co-Publishing and development of new products.Asiasoft as the first company to officially licensed an online game for Vietnam. Gunbound, a casual online game developed by Softnyx was launched in January 2005 and till today the game remained as one of the most success launched in Vietnam with over 4 millions registered. Asiasoft scored another first when we were the only company to launch our second online game from Taiwan TSOnline in April 2005. in June 2006 we Open Beta our 3rd game “Yulgang” (Hiep Khach Giang Ho) developed by KRG and Mgame of Korea, a highly successful game with an estimated 60 million registered in the Asia Pacific Region.Asiasoft continues taking a leading role in the development and publishing of many different types of games. We will continuously be looking at various gaming innovations, service excellence, technological developments and quality production in the areas of Internet and PC Entertainment and enhancing our portfolio of products and services to cater for the local gaming industry.Asiasoft Company Limited works very closely with Asiasoft International a leading pan-Asian world-class game operator and developer located in Bangkok with presence in Singapore and Malaysia. Asiasoft International currently publishes the wide range of online games. Namely, Ragnarok from Gravity, Gunbound from Softnyx, TSOnline from Chinese Gamer, BnB, Maple Story from Nexon, Audition from T3 Entertainment, Granado Espada and Pangya from Hanbitsoft as well as a whole