(87, 'Công Ty TNHH Điện Tử Elek', '', 'cashier@elek.vn', NULL, 'ELEK Electronics Co., Ltd, subsidiary of ELEK FRANCE, designs and manufactures LED Lighting products using LED for more than 6 years. High power LED enable solid-state lighting solutions that are more efficient, more reliable and longer-lasting than ever before. LED LIGHTING allow to reduce CO2 emissions, minimize new energy plant expansion and build more environmentally friendly products. With no mercury or lead content, no heat in the light beam and the ability for digital control, ELEK products are ideally suited for a broad range of lighting needs. No longer a light source for the future, LED Lighting products designed by ELEK FRANCE are the light source for today&rsquo;s lighting solutions. ELEK FRANCE design SMARTHOME solutions for lighting including Controllers and Softwares developed on a large range of Platforms including: PC, APPLE Computer, Iphone, Ipad, Android.\r\n\r\nELEK LED LIGHTING products deliver:\r\n\r\n- Exceptionally long life, longer than any conventional light source\r\n\r\n- Environmentally friendly technology\r\n\r\n- Lower total ownership costs and reduced energy consumption\r\n\r\n- The most robust light source\r\n\r\n- Vivid saturated colors without filters\r\n\r\n- Directed light for increased system efficiency\r\n\r\n- Low voltage solutions\r\n\r\n- Cold start applications', 'Số 1, QL 1K, Tân Hòa, Đông Hòa, Dĩ An, Bình Dương', '', 0),
