(124, 'Glass Egg Digital Media', 'www.glassegg.com', 'recruitment@glassegg.com', NULL, 'Glass Egg is a game developer and art production facility based in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. Over the last 14 years the company has developed a unique set of skills in a unique working environment that enables us to create games and provide related services with a significantly improved level of efficiency\r\n\r\nOur clients are many of the leading companies in game industry in the world such as: Microsoft, Ubisoft, EA, BandaiNamco, Codemasters, KLAB, Simbin, Rebellion, Playground, Foundation 9, to name just a few. Our developers and graphic designers develop, design and code the 3D visual and movement environments for top games played by millions of people across the world.\r\n\r\nWe are now expanding into a new challenge: Mobile Game, Apps &amp; Software Development. We&rsquo;ve launched two App Store games for iPad: Art Of Darkness and Tap Pet Party. GlassEgg has cherished the ambitious social networking project: a dating website called Oakclub.\r\n\r\nWe are searching for talented people to join us on our new adventures.\r\n\r\nPlease send us your information and join us, today!\r\n\r\nWe always welcome candidates with strong background, passion, high energy and eagerness to learn. We will train and set you up for success.\r\n\r\nWebsite: www.glassegg.com\r\n\r\nCompany Size: 200 &ndash; 500\r\n\r\nEmail: recruitment@glassegg.com', 'tầng 17, tòa nhà Ree, 9 Đoàn Văn Bơ, Quận 4', '', 0),
